---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center mt-4 lg:mt-0">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Das OSI-Modell</h1>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto max-w-4xl w-full">
      <table class="border border-gray-300 w-full min-w-full">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-200">
            <th class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">OSI-Schicht Nr.</th>
            <th class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Name (Englisch)</th>
            <th class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Name (Deutsch)</th>
            <th class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Verwendete Protokolle</th>
            <th class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Verwendete Adressen</th>
            <th class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Mögliche Fehler</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">7</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Application</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Anwendung</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">HTTP, FTP, SMTP</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">N/A</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Falsche Datendarstellung, unzureichende Zugriffsrechte</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">6</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Presentation</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Darstellung</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">SSL, TLS, JPEG, ASCII</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">N/A</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Fehlende Datenkonvertierung</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">5</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Session</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Sitzung</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">NetBIOS, RPC</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">N/A</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Abgebrochene Sitzungen</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">4</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Transport</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Transport</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">TCP, UDP</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Port-Nummern</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Paketverlust, falsche Segmentierung</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">3</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Network</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Vermittlung</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">IP, ICMP</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">IP-Adressen</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Routing-Fehler, Adressenkonflikte</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">2</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Data Link</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Sicherung</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Ethernet, PPP</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">MAC-Adressen</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Kollisionsfehler, Frame-Verlust</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">1</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Physical</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Bitübertragung</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Ethernet, USB, WLAN</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">N/A</td>
            <td class="border px-2 py-2 text-xs lg:px-4 lg:text-sm">Signalverlust, physische Schäden</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 max-w-4xl">
      <strong>Tipp:</strong> Um die Namen der OSI-Schichten in Deutsch zu lernen,
      können Sie diesen Satz verwenden:
      <br />
      <strong>A</strong>lle <strong>d</strong>eutsche
      <strong>S</strong>tudenten <strong>t</strong>rinken
      <strong>v</strong>erschiedene <strong>S</strong>orten
      <strong>B</strong>ier.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
